<br>
You would zone in and get swamped by tells even though I had pretty bad equipment for my level and was only level 45.   Most beggers would follow me around so I would attack the bard and root her.   I found that at least half of the beggers would heal me, nuke the bard, or hit the bard.   Then they would die instantly as they would get aggro when running to the bard.<br>
<br>
I used to hate beggers when I first played but after a while I learned alot of great tricks that were not against the rules to mess with them.   I miss my druid the most for this, I never seem to get begged except for the odd beg for a port when they don't realize an outrider is a ranger. <p><Font size="-1" color="green"><u>Caan</u><BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=90906">58 Dark Elf Ranger<BR><A HREF="http://www.titansofsaryrn.com">Titans of Saryrn</a>
